pos_examples: Now, saw board socket into medium part kumquat_8 using saw kumquat with awood screen, surface object_50, changing size from aboardsize yew to aboardsize yew_53 through aboardsize yew_53_66.
(do-saw-medium socket kumquat_8 kumquat screen object_50 yew yew_53_66 yew_53)

Once you are done, please saw board socket into large part kumquat_8 using saw kumquat with awood screen, surface dress_red, changing size from aboardsize yew to aboardsize yew_30 through aboardsize yew_48 and aboardsize yew_30_82.
(do-saw-large socket kumquat_8 kumquat screen dress_red yew yew_30_82 yew_48 yew_30)

First, load board socket into highspeed-saw fire and then saw board socket into small part kumquat_8 using saw kumquat with awood screen, surface dress_red, changing size from aboardsize yew_30 to aboardsize yew_30_79.

(load-highspeed-saw socket fire)
(do-saw-small socket kumquat_8 kumquat screen dress_red yew_30 yew_30_79)

The next step is to do grind on part kumquat_8 using grinder frame_9 to change surface from surface object_50 to verysmooth, color from acolour roof_11 to natural, and treatment from treatmentstatus star_213 to treatmentstatus star_213_43.
(do-grind kumquat_8 frame_9 object_50 roof_11 star_213 star_213_43)
